WEBVTT

00:00.995 --> 00:03.362
Gather around,
glorious turd monsters,

00:03.397 --> 00:06.566
and feast your eyes on
what I hold in this hand:

00:06.567 --> 00:08.768
the future of movement...
a hoverboard.

00:08.769 --> 00:10.103
I don't understand those things.

00:10.104 --> 00:11.971
Is walking really
so hard for you?

00:12.006 --> 00:14.273
Oh, Ames, walking's a nightmare.

00:14.308 --> 00:15.308
Yeah, Amy.

00:15.309 --> 00:19.512
Now, friends, eat
my space dust.

00:19.513 --> 00:20.599
[groans]

00:21.649 --> 00:25.151
Okay, a little harder to control
than I thought.

00:25.152 --> 00:26.853
Okay, there we go.
Whoo!

00:26.854 --> 00:28.154
Think I'm getting
the hang of it.

00:28.155 --> 00:29.855
No, I'm not!
[all yell]

00:29.890 --> 00:30.890
[laughs]

00:32.393 --> 00:34.493
I'm all right.

00:35.796 --> 00:36.862
[whimpering]

00:36.897 --> 00:38.531
[yelling] No!

00:38.532 --> 00:39.531
[crash] Ow!

00:39.533 --> 00:41.534
I'm doing it!
[applause]

00:41.535 --> 00:43.036
I'm doing it!

00:43.037 --> 00:44.037
You got this?

00:44.038 --> 00:45.338
No, I do not got this, Terry!

00:45.339 --> 00:46.740
Don't let go of me!

00:46.741 --> 00:48.842
The future of movement is now!

00:48.843 --> 00:49.968
Whoa!

